title: Episode Seventeen: Season One Recap!
description:
Thanks to all you Psych-O's out there who have been a part of this since the beginning and to all our new listeners as well! We wouldn't be here without you!

In this episode, Tim & Maggie have a major love fest and give thanks and gratitude to fans, friends, family and more! We also put together some of our favorite moments from the pod for you guys to relive as well! Tons of pineapple goodness!
